<body>
    <h1>Reservation Created</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"2b571f9dbe3b"><strong>Component type:</strong> Trigg=
er</p>
<p local-id=3D"04ec1701da47"><strong>Category:</strong> Reservations</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"e8709526dc45" id=3D"ReservationCreated-Overview">Overview</=
h2>
<p local-id=3D"3fe6c4a38200">The <strong>Reservation Created</strong> trigg=
er fires automatically whenever a new reservation is created in your proper=
ty. It serves as the starting point of a workflow, providing detailed infor=
mation about the newly created reservation and its associated guest.</p>
<p local-id=3D"2eb304fa4925">This trigger has no input fields to configure =
=E2=80=94 simply add it to your workflow and it will start listening for ne=
w reservations. When a reservation is created, the component outputs all re=
levant reservation and guest details on the <strong>out</strong> port, whic=
h can then be used by subsequent steps in your workflow.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"76bade3e-9fa8-4144-b047-1efc9ac7c602">
<h2 local-id=3D"1c663f4002b5" id=3D"ReservationCreated-InputFields">Input F=
ields</h2>
<p local-id=3D"dd5e16b8e66a">This component is a trigger and does not have =
any input fields. It activates automatically when a new reservation is crea=
ted in your property.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"fdcdb199-bd54-417b-9bcb-776986c9d47d">
<h2 local-id=3D"bae2880e5b74" id=3D"ReservationCreated-OutputFields">Output=
 Fields</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0d1f6d761d59">When a new reservation is created, the followi=
ng values are available on the <strong>out</strong> output port for use in =
subsequent workflow steps:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"02585f137217" id=3D"ReservationCreated-ReservationDetails">=
Reservation Details</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"756e3088-c5f9-4af3-bd35-5a1=
870fdd08a" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"bb231f3d-16b9-41d5-b830-e0552c67a410">
<th data-local-id=3D"5ec003d9-a915-4cf5-a77f-05aa4cadeee8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
