<td data-local-id=3D"a043338e-d4ca-4ff0-92c7-bc23eca53033" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2909426b62cc">The unique identifier of the space (room) assi=
gned to the reservation. May be empty if no space has been assigned yet.</p=
